01:02:31.789 --> 01:02:33.417
<i>Dean-o's staying with him.</i>

01:02:33.458 --> 01:02:35.960
<i>If he would have narced, they</i>
<i>would have taken him already.</i>

01:02:36.002 --> 01:02:38.213
<i>Who's to say that he</i>
